         <abstract>
            <ab>The Canon of the church of <placeName ref="LOC4885Mualla">Muʿallaqa</placeName> is an introduction to the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2384Taamme"/>. It was purportedly translated from Arabic in <date when="1441"/> at the order of <persName ref="PRS10626ZaraY"/>,
            but no Arabic version is known. It can be followed or preceded by
            <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3584Intro"/>.</ab>
         </abstract>
